rafthouse is designed to work with all of Layers&#8217; header options including boxed, full-width and sticky layouts.</p>\\n<ul>\\n    <li>Center Top</li>\\n    <li>Inline</li>\\n    <li>Logo Left / Menu Right</li>\\n    <li>Menu Left / Logo Right</li>\\n    <li>Logo Top</li>\\n    <li>Header Over (applies to all layout options)</li>\\n    <li>Boxed / Unboxed headers</li>\\n</ul>\\n\\n<p>\\n    <strong>\\n        This theme comes packed with <a href=\\"http://www.layerswp.com/storekit/\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">StoreKit</a>, worth $21, for Free!\\n    </strong>\\n</p>\\n\\n<h3 id=\\"item-description__what-is-layers\\"><strong>What is Layers?</strong></h3>\\n<p>\\n    Layers is a free <a href=\\"http://www.layerswp.com/\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">WordPress Site Builder</a> that allows you to build beautiful websites\\n    through an interface that is so simple you&#8217;ll be a pro the first time you use it.\\n</p>\\n\\n<ul>\\n    <li>\\n        <strong>Built into WordPress. Not on top.</strong><br />\\n        Layers is activated as a WordPress theme and works directly with the built-in WordPress Customizer.\\n    </li>\\n    <li>\\n        <strong>Point &#38; Click Interface </strong><br />\\n        A code-free interface gives you control over the content and aesthetics of your site while still maintaining good design fundamentals.\\n    </li>\\n    <li>\\n        <strong>Open Source &#38; Extendable</strong><br />\\n        <a href=\\"http://www.layerswp.com/download\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Download Layers</a> and create anything you want, from gorgeous themes to powerful extensions, or contribute to the core on GitHub.\\n    </li>\\n</ul>\\n\\n<h3 id=\\"item-description__code-free-site-building\\"><a href=\\"http://www.layerswp.com/features/\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\"><strong>Code Free Site Building</strong></a></h3>\\n<p>\\n    With Layers you don&#8217;t need a degree in HTML and CSS to get the design you desire. With preset layouts and the easy to use Design Bar, you never 